4. Structural Breaks: A Cumulative Sum (cusum6) test is used to identify instability patterns or regime shifts across the historical timeline.
(Refer graph folder)

 cusum6 lnoutput lnarea lnprice lnfertilizer lnrainfall lncpi


5. Lag Selection: Executes Vector Autoregressive Lag Order Selection Criteria (varsoc) individually per variable to determine the optimal lag structure based on AIC, BIC, and HQIC.

