6. Stationarity Testing: Implements Augmented Dickey-Fuller (dfuller) tests incorporating trends and explicit lag adjustments to determine each variable's order of integration (\(I(0)\) or \(I(1)\)).

. dfuller lnoutput, lags(1) trend regress

Augmented Dickey–Fuller test for unit root

Variable: lnoutput                         Number of obs  = 33
                                           Number of lags =  1

H0: Random walk with or without drift

                                       Dickey–Fuller
                   Test      -------- critical value ---------
              statistic           1%           5%          10%
--------------------------------------------------------------
 Z(t)            -3.458       -4.306       -3.568       -3.221
--------------------------------------------------------------
MacKinnon approximate p-value for Z(t) = 0.0442.

Regression table
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
