7. Generating first differences variables

. gen dlnarea       = D.lnarea
(1 missing value generated)

. gen dlnfertilizer = D.lnfertilizer
(1 missing value generated)

. gen dlnrainfall   = D.lnrainfall
(1 missing value generated)

. gen dlncpi        = D.lncpi
(1 missing value generated)


8.  ARDL Modeling & Cointegration

. ardl lnoutput lnprice dlnfertilizer dlnarea dlnrainfall dlncpi if tin(1991,2025), ec1 maxlags(2) regstore(ecre
> g)

